author: ggregory
msg: Test order should not matter. When this test class is invoked from Eclipse for example, while running all tests in the project, it will fail. This change extracts the static block code into a method to be invoked from the test set up and tear down methods. Also make sure we do disable everything in the test. The refactoring also renames the svar all (all what?) to disableAll. I'm not sure why we even need this ivar...
